The C4 community exists in a few different places, and for good reason. We could host our own code, our own forums, and have email bulletins, but instead we tried to go a bit of a different route.

We've chosen 4 places to keep you up to date with new releases, code samples / examples / tutorials / ..., news and pictures. 

Stack Overflow
--------------
image::community/stackoverflow.png["Stack Overflow"]

Instead of a wiki or forum that we'll be updating and maintaining, we've decided to use link:http://stackoverflow.com[Stack Overflow] as the place to ask questions and have discussions about programming.

