The C4 Tag
~~~~~~~~~~
Every question asked on S.O. has at least one, but usually several tags associated with it. The C4 Framework has its own tag, which you can check out here: link:http://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/c4[C4 on S.O.]

You can read all the other posts about C4, upvote them, contribute to answers and so on... 

When you ask a question about C4 you can tag it and the rest of the C4 community will get a little notification. We're pretty eager to answer questions that pop up, so you should get a response fairly quickly.

S.O. Tutorial
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
We've written a tutorial for getting started with Stack Overflow. There are a few steps to getting up and running with the site, though nothing to daunting. 

We also describe a few things like setting up a logo (using Gravatar if you want), and the etiquette for asking questions and posting answers.

link:stackoverflow.php[Stack Overflow Tutorial]

